      <title>花旗新任银行主管获得 4100 万美元股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/citi-s-new-banking-chief-gets-41-million-in-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团今年早些时候聘请 Viswas Raghavan 担任其新银行业务主管，并已向高管授予了价值约 4100 万美元的股份（按当前价值计算）。Sonali Basak 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/citi-s-new-banking-chief-gets-41-million-in-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:42:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行计划为赛诺菲消费品业务出售提供 60 亿欧元债务融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/banks-plan-6-billion-debt-financing-for-sanofi-consumer-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，包括高盛集团和摩根士丹利在内的多家银行正在为赛诺菲消费者健康部门的潜在买家提供超过 60 亿欧元（65 亿美元）的债务融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/banks-plan-6-billion-debt-financing-for-sanofi-consumer-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于建筑成本上升，ADM 放弃与 LG 化学的合资项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/adm-scraps-ventures-with-lg-chem-as-construction-costs-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于成本过高，农业巨头阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司已停止与 LG 化学有限公司的合资生产生物塑料等植物产品的材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/adm-scraps-ventures-with-lg-chem-as-construction-costs-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:29:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Evercore 的 Emanuel 表示市场感觉良好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/the-market-feels-good-says-evercore-s-emanuel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore ISI 首席股票、衍生品和量化策略师朱利安·伊曼纽尔 (Julian Emanuel) 表示，目前这是一个股票市场，而不是股票市场。他谈到了盈利乐观情绪，并表示美联储 7 月份降息的可能性不大。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/the-market-feels-good-says-evercore-s-emanuel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:29:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国消费者信心指数跌至八个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/us-consumer-sentiment-slides-to-eight-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国消费者信心指数 7 月份意外从 68.2 降至 66，跌至八个月以来的最低水平。Matt Miller 报道了“彭博未平仓合约”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-12/us-consumer-sentiment-slides-to-eight-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:24:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债权人通过新债券销售反击资产剥离</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/creditors-fight-back-against-asset-stripping-in-new-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在宽松货币时代盛行的宽松债券文件使得投资者在最近的债务交易中容易遭受资产剥离。现在他们正在反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/creditors-fight-back-against-asset-stripping-in-new-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统在致命抗议活动后任命代理警察局长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/kenya-president-names-acting-police-boss-after-deadly-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚反税示威游行遭到警方残酷镇压，造成至少 41 人死亡三周后，总统威廉·鲁托周五任命了新的安全负责人，试图平息东非工业化程度最高的经济体的动乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/kenya-president-names-acting-police-boss-after-deadly-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:16:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空业前景黯淡 空客启动成本节约计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/airbus-starts-cost-saving-plan-as-aviation-industry-turns-gloomy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了应对供应链限制和不断上升的费用，空中客车公司已着手实施一项计划，以提高业绩并控制成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/airbus-starts-cost-saving-plan-as-aviation-industry-turns-gloomy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 14:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
